casebody.data:
Hadden, Respondent, v. McGuire, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County,

General Term.

May 12, 1892.) Action by Alexander Hadden against Michael McGuire.

Argued before Bookstaver and Bischoff, JJ.

Charles Be Kay Townsend, for appellant. J. C. Wolf, for respondent.

Ho .opinion. Motion for reargument denied, with $10 costs. For decision on appeal, see 19 N. Y. Supp. 1011.
